    "The effect of this book was to drive the discipline as a whole toward archival research.": [],
    "Haskell was called to Oxford University in 1967 to replace <a href=\"/winde\">Edgar Wind</a>.": [],
    "At Oxford, he changed research focus, examining the neglected (and disparaged) French academic art of the 19th century.": [],
    "The book he produced, the result of the Wrightsman lectures at New York University, became another seminal work in an ignored area.": [
